Package Summary
Package
Description
Agents
Agents contains all maze-related agent classes and those closely related (e.g.
Display
Display contains classes related to graphical representation: the dynamic HealthBar, and all locations of game assets.
Fixed
Fixed contains all maze-related objects that do not move.
Game
Game stores all high-level logic: the game back-end (Maze), the GUI representations (Game), and several related high-level objects (Cell, Clock, GameNode, MazeObject)
Levels
Levels stores the logic for loading levels, both manually from classes and from txt files.
Pages
Package is used to store different screens that the client transitions between.
